Package bean

This package contains java beans, that means class, that contains default constructor, getters and setters to all field.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Audio
    JPA entity that maps audio details to the DB
    AudioPostSuccessMessage
    Used to build success audio creation message
    Credentials
    Base class that stores credentials (e-mail and password), use also as JPA entity in connection with derived User class
    ErrorMessage
    Holds error message
    Project
    JPA entity that holds song project details
    ProjectPatchSuccessMessage
    Represents project partial update (patch) response object
    ProjectPostSuccessMessage
    Consists of information that need to be send back to the user when project had been successfully created
    Sample
    JPA Entity that describes single sample
    SuccessMessage
    Utility class that could be used to produce nice success message in response
    Track
    JPA entity that contains information about project tracks
    User
    JPA entity that maps user details to the DB.

Package bean Description

This package contains java beans, that means class, that contains default constructor, getters and setters to all field. Also, these classes are serializable. Inside this package you can find generally JPA entities, but there are some utility classes for http responses.
